text: Melatonin helps my dog with the fireworks

Cannabis oil

text: Your vet will have a better idea of dosage that I could guess. Meagan's dog is a yorkie so  we're going to give her a whole drop where the vet said to give Moose "the whole dang bottle maybe?"
